  {
    "client_msg_id": "678a48bf-d91d-4414-8148-962331afa3dd",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "Another way to put it: I think communities of empowered people are a _much_ harder problem than empowered individuals. And it's impossible to achieve the former without the latter; communities just have a way of disempowering people by enabling laziness and so on. It's worth tightening focus for the first 20 years.",
    "user": "UCUSW7WVD",
    "ts": "1566237670.150600",
    "team": "T5TCAFTA9",
